Package: RedditSentiment
Type: Package
Title: Reddit Comment Sentiment Analysis 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eric Zarycki
Maintainer: The package maintainer <ericzarycki@usf.edu>
Description:  The RedditSentiment package provides tools for analyzing sentiment in Reddit comments.
    It includes functions for fetching Reddit comments using the Reddit API, preprocessing the text 
    data to remove noise and irrelevant information, and performing sentiment analysis using 
    other R packages.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
